 Sheri has done a great job of leading the Product Control Group over the p=
ast 14 months.  Sheri is committed to see that her team continues to work c=
losely with Operations to ensure that any changes in Enron's e-commerce bus=
inesses that may impact trading operations are shared with us.  We look for=
