As of August 1, 2001 Axia Energy, LP has changed its name to
Entergy-Koch Trading, LP (EKT).  The changing of our name will not
affect our business in any way, but will allow our trading and marketing
groups to have a clearer association with our parent companies.  Our
corporate structure and financial position will remain the same.  

In association, email addresses have changed.  Please use the following
format for addressing emails to Entergy-Koch Trading, LP.

first.last@entergykoch.com

Your email has been forwarded to the appropriate recipients, but please
make this change on all future correspondence.

